OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of mostly
OL,6,Flight rain clearing eastward, with
OL,7,Fdrier and brighter intervals
OL,8,Fdeveloping from around midday.
OL,9,FRemaining cloudy along the south
OL,10,Fcoast. Heavy showery rain arriving in
OL,11,Fthe northwest into the afternoon. Mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome early evening bright
OL,14,Fspells possible in the north and east,
OL,15,Fthough showers further south and west.
OL,16,FTurning cloudy overnight with rain,
OL,17,Fheavy at times, spreading east. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
