OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy to start, gradually
OL,6,Fturning brighter from the west as rain
OL,7,Fclears eastward. A chance of showers
OL,8,Ffor a time in the afternoon. Light
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,12,Fwinds Sunday, with rain spreading
OL,13,Feast. Breezy Monday with bright spells
OL,14,Fand a chance of rain. Likely dry but
OL,15,Fcloudy Tuesday with light winds.
OL,16,FTemperatures a little above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
